Synchronize

Passive Ability

When an opposing Pokémon decreases this Pokémon's movement speed, also decreases that opposing Pokémon's movement speed by 40% for 3s; or, when an opposing Pokémon inflicts a damage-over-time status condition on this Pokémon, also inflicts a damage-over time effect on that opposing Pokémon for 3s (8s CD).

15% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 15

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and decreasing their Sp. Def by 10% for 2s.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

44% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 180

Confusion

Move 1

4.50s Ranged

The user fires a psychic bolt in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon hit and decreasing their movement speed by 35% for 1s.

83% SpA + 19 x (Level - 1) + 350

Confusion Upgrade Choices

Psychic

7.50s Ranged

The user launches a psychic bolt in the designated direction which blasts on the first opposing Pokémon hit or after traveling max distance, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect. The blast creates a lingering field that slowly moves forward, dealing damage over time to opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and decreasing their movement speed by 50% for 1s (up to 5 hits). Each time this move hits opposing Pokémon, their Sp. Def is decreased by 25% for 4s (maximum 75%).

85% SpA + 16 x (Level - 1) + 440

8.5% SpA + 2 x (Level - 1) + 44

Reduces this move's cooldown by 1s.

Moonblast

7.00s Ranged

The user dashes back slightly and launches a blast of moonlight in the designated direction which bursts into a cone behind the first opposing Pokémon hit, stunning that opposing Pokémon for 1.2s and damaging all opposing Pokémon in the cone area of effect, including the target.

66% SpA + 13 x (Level - 1) + 340

Grants the user a shield for 3s when launching the blast.

60% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 300

Teleport

Move 2

9.00s Dash

The user readies a boosted attack and warps forward to the designated location.

When this move is learned, passively increases the damage of Synchronize, auto attacks, and Confusion by 15% until this move is replaced.

Teleport Upgrade Choices

Psyshock

11.00s Area

The user channels at a designated area relative to their position before launching three attacks in succession, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and reducing the user's moves' cooldowns by 15% with each attack that hits.

The user is able to attack and move freely while channeling this move.

90% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 430

Increases the damage of the next attack to hit each time an attack hits an opposing Pokémon.

90% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 430

95% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 451

100% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 475

Future Sight

9.00s Area

The user sets a delayed explosion at the designated area, damaging opposing Pokémon when the delayed explosion hits. If this move hits a Pokémon from the opposing team, the cooldown of this move is reduced by 75% and the user's movement speed is increased by 40% for 1.5s.

156.45% SpA + 22 x (Level - 1) + 924

Resets this move's cooldown when it hits a Pokémon from the opposing team.

Fairy Singularity

Unite Move

89s 80000 Hindrance

Unlocks at level 9

The user warps space in the designated area, dealing damage to opposing Pokémon and pulling them toward the center 4 times. As the warped space disappears, it deals increased damage to opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and shoves them away from the center.

66% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 400

33% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 200

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
